
		       Removable Media Utilities
		       =========================


Topics
------

  1. Introduction
  2. License
  3. Install
  4. Usage
  A. Credits
  B. Bugs
  C. Resources


1. Introduction
---------------

This package  installs scripts  to handle  removable media  devices: USB
pendrives, CD-ROMs.


